Detailed Description

GoogleIMA3.

Copyright (c) 2013 Google Inc. All rights reserved.

This file provides error codes that are raised by the SDK and declares the IMAAdError class.

Enumeration Type Documentation

enum IMAErrorCode

Possible error codes raised while loading or playing ads.

Enumerator
kIMAError_VAST_MALFORMED_RESPONSE 

The ad response was not recognized as a valid VAST ad.

kIMAError_UNKNOWN_AD_RESPONSE 

The ad response was not understood and cannot be parsed.

kIMAError_VAST_LOAD_TIMEOUT 

The VAST URI provided, or a VAST URI provided in a subsequent Wrapper element, was either unavailable or reached a timeout, as defined by the video player.

The timeout is 8 seconds for initial VAST requests and 4 seconds for each subsequent Wrapper.

kIMAError_VAST_TOO_MANY_REDIRECTS 

The maximum number of VAST wrapper redirects has been reached.

kIMAError_VAST_INVALID_URL 

At least one VAST wrapper loaded and a subsequent wrapper or inline ad load has resulted in a 404 response code.

kIMAError_VIDEO_PLAY_ERROR 

There was an error playing the video ad.

kIMAError_VAST_MEDIA_LOAD_TIMEOUT 

Failed to load media assets from a VAST response.

The default timeout for media loading is 15 seconds.

kIMAError_VAST_LINEAR_ASSET_MISMATCH 

Assets were found in the VAST ad response for linear ad, but none of them matched the video player's capabilities.

kIMAError_COMPANION_AD_LOADING_FAILED 

A companion ad failed to load or render.

kIMAError_UNKNOWN_ERROR 

An unexpected error occurred and the cause is not known.

Refer to the inner error for more information.

kIMAError_PLAYLIST_MALFORMED_RESPONSE 

Ads list response was malformed.

kIMAError_FAILED_TO_REQUEST_ADS 

There was a problem requesting ads from the server.

kIMAError_REQUIRED_LISTENERS_NOT_ADDED 

Listener for at least one of the required vast events was not added.

kIMAError_VAST_ASSET_NOT_FOUND 

No assets were found in the VAST ad response.

kIMAError_ADSLOT_NOT_VISIBLE 

The ad slot is not visible on the page.

kIMAError_VAST_EMPTY_RESPONSE 

Empty VAST response.

kIMAError_FAILED_LOADING_AD 

There was an error loading the ad.

kIMAError_INVALID_ARGUMENTS 

Invalid arguments were provided to SDK methods.

kIMAError_API_ERROR 

Generic invalid usage of the API.

kIMAError_IOS_RUNTIME_TOO_OLD 

The version of the runtime is too old.

kIMAError_VIDEO_ELEMENT_USED 

Another VideoAdsManager is still using the video.

It must be unloaded before another ad can play on the same element.

kIMAError_VIDEO_ELEMENT_REQUIRED 

A video element was not specified where it was required.

kIMAError_CONTENT_PLAYHEAD_MISSING 

Content playhead was not passed in, but list of ads has been returned from the server.

enum IMAErrorType

Possible error types while loading or playing ads.

Enumerator
kIMAAdUnknownErrorType 

An unexpected error occured while loading or playing the ads.

This may mean that the SDK wasn't loaded properly.

kIMAAdLoadingFailed 

An error occured while loading the ads.

kIMAAdPlayingFailed 

An error occured while playing the ads.
